339
00:21:04,597 --> 00:21:06,691
Amy.

340
00:21:07,057 --> 00:21:08,855
Bien. En fin...

341
00:21:09,435 --> 00:21:12,188
Voy a volver, Amy. Voy a volver.

342
00:21:13,564 --> 00:21:14,606
Y voy a...

343
